      "instruction": "<p>While the chicken is cooking, dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> in 200ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> <span class=\"text-purple\">[300ml] </span>[400ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p>",
