    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>roasted</strong> <strong>garlic paste</strong> to the pan with your <strong>finely chopped tomatoes</strong>, <strong>diced apricots</strong>,<strong> sultanas</strong>, <strong>chopped tomato </strong>and 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[150ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[200ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Bring to the boil and cook for a further 6-8 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>fruity Moroccan-style chicken stew</strong></p>",
